{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"grid-template-areas","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>grid-template-areas</code></strong> CSS 属性是网格区域 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Grid_Areas\">grid areas</a> 在 CSS 中的特定命名。</p><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"390\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/css/grid-template-areas.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>\n<p>网格区块 (grid areas) 和网格项 (grid item) 沒有关联，但是它们可以和一些网格定位属性 (grid-placement properties) 关联起来，比如<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row-start\"><code>grid-row-start</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>， <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row-end\"><code>grid-row-end</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>， <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column-start\"><code>grid-column-start</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>和<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column-end\"><code>grid-column-end</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>；也可以和一些速记 (shorthands) 属性关联起来，比如<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row\"><code>grid-row</code></a>，<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column\"><code>grid-column</code></a> 和 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-area\"><code>grid-area</code></a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax语法","title":"Syntax[语法]","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">/* Keyword value */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-template-areas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* &lt;string&gt; values */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-template-areas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"a b\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* 一行 两列 */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-template-areas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"a b b\"</span>\n                     <span class=\"token string\">\"a c d\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* 两行 三列 */</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* Global values */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-template-areas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> inherit<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* 继承 */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-template-areas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> initial<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* 默认值 */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid-template-areas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> unset<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* 未设置 */</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"values可选值","title":"Values[可选值]","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"none\"><code>none</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>网格容器没有定义任何的网格区块 (grid areas)。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"string\"><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/string\"><code>&lt;string&gt;</code></a>+</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>每一个给定的字符串会生成一行，一个字符串中用空格分隔的每一个单元 (cell) 会生成一列。多个同名的，跨越相邻行或列的单元称为网格区块 (grid area)。非矩形的网格区块是无效的。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"形式化语法","title":"形式化语法","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">none <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/string\" title=\"\">&lt;string&gt;</a><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#plus\" title=\"Plus: the entity may occur one or several times\">+</a></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>section</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>page<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>header</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Header<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>header</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>nav</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Navigation<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>nav</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Main area<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>footer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Footer<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>footer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css","title":"CSS","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">#page</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* 1.设置 display 为 grid */</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 250px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-template-areas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"head head\"</span>\n                       <span class=\"token string\">\"nav  main\"</span>\n                       <span class=\"token string\">\"nav  foot\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* 2.区域划分 当前为 三行 两列 */</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-template-rows</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50px 1fr 30px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* 3.各区域 宽高设置 */</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-template-columns</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 150px 1fr<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">#page &gt; header</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-area</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> head<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* 4. 指定当前元素所在的区域位置，从 grid-template-areas 选取值 */</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #8ca0ff<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">#page &gt; nav</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-area</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> nav<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #ffa08c<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">#page &gt; main</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-area</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> main<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #ffff64<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">#page &gt; footer</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-area</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> foot<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #8cffa0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"结果","title":"结果","isH3":true,"content":"<iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"示例 sample\" id=\"frame_示例\" width=\"100%\" height=\"250px\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas/_sample_.%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-grid/#grid-template-areas-property","title":"CSS Grid Layout Module Level 3"}],"query":"css.properties.grid-template-areas"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"properties\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/initial_value\">初始值</a></th><td><code>none</code></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">适用元素</th><td>grid containers</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/inheritance\">是否是继承属性</a></th><td>否</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/computed_value\">计算值</a></th><td>as specified</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Animation type</th><td>discrete</td></tr></tbody></table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"css.properties.grid-template-areas","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>相关 CSS 属性：<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\"><code>grid-template-rows</code></a>、<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\"><code>grid-template-columns</code></a>、<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template\"><code>grid-template</code></a></li>\n  <li>Grid Layout 指南*：<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Grid_Template_Areas\">Grid template areas</a>*</li>\n  <li>视频教程*：<a href=\"https://gridbyexample.com/video/grid-template-areas/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Grid Template Areas</a>*</li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS\"><strong>CSS</strong></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Reference\"><strong>CSS Reference</strong></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout\">CSS Grid Layout</a></li>\n  <li><strong>Guides</str